## How much does counseling cost?

The cost of counseling services in Houston varies widely, typically ranging from $75 to $200 per session. Factors influencing this include the therapist's qualifications, session length, and the type of therapy provided. Many practitioners offer sliding scale fees, making therapy more accessible for those in need.\
